text: Ceroplesis aenescens is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Fairmaire in 1893. It is known from Ethiopia.BioLib.cz - Ceroplesis aenescens. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Ceroplesis Category:Beetles described in 1893
title: Ceroplesis aenescens
